name: Femboy Hooters: Visual Novel (WIP)
description:
This game is in early production. Anything present in the game might be subject to change in the future. 

---

In this cute visual novel, you enter a classic, family-owned Femboy Hooters and are greeted by the waitress, Astolfo! Go down different paths in the game to be achieve different endings and secret plot that exposes the true story.

Meet such great people like the Terminator!
